typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		agaagaid as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select agaagaid from dwh_stage.p_agatable where agabusndiv =1',
	format: 'query') ~> agatable
source(output(
		source_code_key as string,
		target_code as string,
		target_description as string,
		code_type as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select source_code_key,target_code,target_description,code_type from dwh_stage.t_crossreference where source_system = \'PARIS\' and code_type_id = 167',
	format: 'query') ~> Tcross
source(output(
		lablabid as string,
		labmainev as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select lablabid,labmainev from dwh_stage.p_labtable',
	format: 'query') ~> Labtable
source(output(
		inainaid as string,
		inaagaid as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select inainaid,inaagaid from dwh_stage.p_inatable',
	format: 'query') ~> Inatable
source(output(
		icaicaid as string,
		icainaid as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select icaicaid,icainaid from dwh_stage.p_icatable',
	format: 'query') ~> Icatable
source(output(
		lcalcaid as string,
		lcaicaid as string,
		lcalabid as string,
		lcaagaid as string,
		lcalossco as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select lcalcaid,lcaicaid,lcalabid,lcaagaid,lcalossco from dwh_stage.p_lcatable',
	format: 'query') ~> Lcatable
source(output(
		falfalid as string,
		falclmcat as string,
		fallcaid as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select falfalid,falclmcat,fallcaid from dwh_stage.p_faltable where falinout= \'I\'',
	format: 'query') ~> faltable
agatable, Inatable join(agaagaid == inaagaid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> AgaIna
AgaIna, Icatable join(inainaid == icainaid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> InaIca
InaIca, Lcatable join(icaicaid == lcaicaid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> IcaLca
IcaLca, Labtable join(lcalabid == lablabid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LcaLab
LcaLab, faltable join(lcaicaid == fallcaid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LcaFal
